CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 13, 1954, pg. 12 reads: " More Queen Contestants - Another group of Pittsburgh teen-agers who are clamoring to wear the crown of Hill City Queen includes, left to right...Maribeth Jones...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Maribeth Jones wearing dark neck scarf, light colored long sleeved blouse, and striped skirt, posed in front of light colored background in Harris Studio for Hill City Teen Queen contest
